item.title: CVE-2020-5686|2024-08-04T08:39:25.708Z -- nec%20corporation -- univerge%20sv9500%2Fsv8500%20series
item.description: Incorrect implementation of authentication algorithm issue in UNIVERGE SV9500 series from V1 to V7and SV8500 series from S6 to S8 allows an attacker to access the remote system maintenance feature and obtain the information by sending a specially crafted request to a specific URL.

item.title: CVE-2020-5685|2024-08-04T08:39:25.664Z -- nec%20corporation -- univerge%20sv9500%2Fsv8500%20series
item.description: UNIVERGE SV9500 series from V1 to V7and SV8500 series from S6 to S8 allows an attacker to execute arbitrary OS commands or cause a denial-of-service (DoS) condition by sending a specially crafted request to a specific URL.
